name: AK_420
description:
I mint this on 30Sept, the day where Indonesian take their time to commemorate a historical event we call G30S PKI. This edition of my AK_420 has that local camo pattern uniform worn by the Indonesian military nowadays. 
 
This Artwork is dedicated to reminding us all about that historical event happen in Indonesia that not many people are talking about. (of course: weed is illegal in here, I know. But knowledge is not).
